snippet.title: Halodoom Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Halodoom is a project about the past and the present colliding. A new story in the Halo universe told using the Doom engine.

Halodoom COS is still a work in progress, but you can still download the original beta 1.0 here! http://forestbear.net/projects/halodoom/


Follow us on Twitter : https://twitter.com/ForestBearMedia
Like us on Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/ForestBearStudios
Join our forum : http://www.forestbear.net

Disclaimer:
Halodoom Official Trailer was created under Microsoft's "Game Content Usage Rules" using music from "Halo 3 :ODST" and "Halo Reach" © Microsoft Corporation.
